ActCanadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999
PrecisRegulations Amending the GASOLINE REGULATIONS by exempting gasoline intended for use in competition vehicles (i.e., automobiles, motorcycles, snowmobiles and motorboats used for racing purposes) from the otherwise applicable limits on the concentration of lead in gasoline, until January 1, 2008.
